## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of historical events. Additionally, the perspectives of enslaved individuals themselves are often underrepresented in historical records, leading to potential gaps in understanding their experiences and agency during the Revolutionary period. Further research into primary sources and scholarly analyses would provide a more nuanced view of the impact of the American Revolution on slavery.